Judicial documents involving national security, juvenile delinquency, divorce proceedings, support or guardianship of minor children, etc., shall not be made public. In
public judgment documents, information concerning personal privacy,
trade secrets, etc., other than the names of the parties, shall also be
deleted from the document.
